		<h2>Keyboard Shortcuts</h2>
		<div class="left">
			<h3>Actions</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>enter: Drops down &rdquo;add new&ldquo; menu</li>

				<li>esc: Exit text field/close popup</li>
				<li>shift + m: New message</li>
				<li>shift + t: New task</li>
				<li>/ or ?: Display shortcut list</li>
				<li>T: Delete / trash</li>
				<li>g then S: Settings</li>

				<li>g then P: Profile</li>
				<li>R: Reply to current messages/task</li>
				<li>U: Subscribe/unsubscribe to task/message thread</li>
				<li>Tab: Tab through items left to right, top to bottom</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="right">

			<h3>Basic</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>arrow up: Previous item</li>
				<li>arrow down: Next item</li>
				<li>arrow left/right: Toggle panel 1 or 2</li>
			</ul>
			<h3>Navigation</h3>

			<ul>
				<li>Q/W/E: Message/task/chat view</li>
				<li>A/Z: Item up/down in panel 1</li>
				<li>S/X: Item up/down in panel 2</li>
				<li>D/C: Item up/down in panel 3</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="clear-fix"></div>
	</div>
